s<OPTION>Brewing (189)<OPTION>Fishing (200)<OPTION>Pottery (123)<OPTION>Smithing (221)<OPTION>Tailoring (43)</SELECT><BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ueumerin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eumerin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wandering Knight</span><br>  Posts: 195<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/15/02 10:05:29 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Updated Paladin Armor sets</span><hr size=1> Here's the message thread over at EQ Traders that details the general armor template.<br><br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub126.ezboard.com/feqtraderscornerfrm13.showMessage?topicID=1393.topic">pub126.ezboard.com/feqtra...1393.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>It compares the stats on the different pieces of armor, and the different types (plate, chain, leather, and cloth equivalent) using general templates.<br>If you're not interested in wading through it all...<br><br>The AC can be picked up from the link up above in the initial post for this thread (AC is identical across the board in each plate piece so far).  The extra stats are listed below (pulled directly from the EQ Traders thread I linked to).  A listed stat means that the stat is present whether or not the armor is imbued.  Imbued means that if the armor is imbued, the additional stats (from imbueing) will add up to that total.<br><br><!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> <br>Chest: 40 hp 40 mana 5 stamina 15 imbued<br>Back: 40 hp 40 mana 15 imbued<br>Legs: 40 hp 40 mana 10 imbued<br>Belt: 40 hp 40 mana 10 imbued<br>Helm: 30 mana 30 hp 10 imbued<br>Wrist: 30 hp 30 mana 5 to all resists 5 imbued<br>Boots: 30 hp 30 mana 5 dex 5 imbued<br>Arms: 30 hp 30 mana 5 imbued<br>Face: 30 hp 30 mana 5 AGI 5 imbued<br>Shoulders: 30 hp 30 mana 5 dex 5 imbued<br>Neck: 25 hp 25 mana 5 agi 5 imbued<br>Hands: 25 mana 25 mana 5 dex 5 imbued<br></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br><br>I could be mistaken, but I think the only cultural that no one has reported a success in as of yet is the Erudite, so its possible that the Erudite will through everyone for a loop (the Erudite Steelsilk was slightly different from the other culturals in the old cultural set).  The main problem is that there is apparently a lack of Erudite tailors with a high enough tailoring to be able to make this stuff.<br> <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=96807 target="web">Eumerin Paxodus</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bpaladinsofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=kleitus>Kleitus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 736<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/30/02 10:34:38 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Updated Paladin Armor sets</span><hr size=1> Finally got around to moving this thread to here.  When I get the chance, I'll add more information to it about the cultural armors and the quests for the other armors.<br><br>This is by no means a complete list for people since it lacks a ton of dropped equipment from the high end mobs. <p>Kleitus <br>Level 54 Deepwater Cavalier of Erudin <br>Xegony</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.showPrevMessage?topicID=62.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.showNextMessage?topicID=62.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladi